spirit:component.spirit:name: design_1_xdma_1_0_pcie4_ip_ibert
spirit:component.spirit:description: The In-System IBERT core is customizable and designed for evaluating and monitoring FPGA transceivers. This core provides eye scan plot for selected GTs and acess to ports related to eyescan and the dynamic reconfiguration port attributes transceivers. Communication logic is also included to allow the design to be run-time accessible through Joint Test Action Group (JTAG). Run-time interaction with this core requires the use of the Vivado serial I/O analyzer feature.

spirit:parameter.spirit:name: C_GTS_USED
spirit:parameter.spirit:description: Indicate whether this transceiver channel is instantiated and enabled for use
